description: Retrieves a configured audience model association within a collaboration.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the configured audience model association belongs to. Accepts a collaboration ID.

parameters.name: configuredAudienceModelAssociationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the configured audience model association that you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: collaborationConfiguredAudienceModelAssociation
nested_items.description: The metadata of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the configured audience model associations belong to. Accepts collaboration ID.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the configured audience model's associated collaboration.

nested_items.name: configuredAudienceModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configure audience model.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the configured audience model association.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The identifier used to reference members of the collaboration. Only supports Amazon Web Services account ID.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the configured audience model association was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the configured audience model association was updated.
